                                        <p>
                                          A new battery-electric-powered Chevy
                                          Equinox EV hits the market this year
                                          alongside the standard gas-powered
                                          <a href="/chevrolet/equinox/"
                                            >Chevrolet Equinox</a
                                          >
                                          SUV. However, the only thing the
                                          Equinox EV shares with the
                                          conventional Equinox is its name. The
                                          two vehicles are based on different
                                          platforms, have different powertrains,
                                          and are likely to appeal to different
