                          <div class="mb-3">
                            <h3 class="heading-4 normal-case mb-1">Overview</h3>
                            <p data-test="vehicleDescription">
                              The 2024 Kia EV9 is a midsize, three-row electric
                              SUV with excellent passenger space, plenty of
                              power, reasonable driving range, and mainstream
                              pricing in a category dominated by expensive
                              luxury brands. The Kia EV9 is a 6-seater vehicle
                              that comes in 5 trim levels. The most popular
                              style is the Land AWD, which starts at $71,395 and
                              comes with an Electric engine and All Wheel Drive.
                            </p>
