                                <p data-test="vehicleDescription">
                                  The 2024 Kia EV9 is a midsize, three-row
                                  electric SUV with excellent passenger space,
                                  plenty of power, reasonable driving range, and
                                  mainstream pricing in a category dominated by
                                  expensive luxury brands. The Kia EV9 is a
                                  6-seater vehicle that comes in 5 trim levels.
                                  The most popular style is the Land AWD, which
                                  starts at $71,395 and comes with an Electric
                                  engine and All Wheel Drive.
                                </p>
