                          <div class="mb-3">
                            <h3 class="heading-4 normal-case mb-1">Overview</h3>
                            <p data-test="vehicleDescription">
                              A stately demeanor and hint of high-octane
                              performance define the 2025 BMW i5 all-electric
                              sedan. It’s not the flashiest EV around, but the
                              i5 is classy and well-rounded. The BMW i5 is a
                              5-seater vehicle that comes in 3 trim levels. The
                              most popular style is the xDrive40, which starts
                              at $71,275 and comes with an Electric engine and
                              All Wheel Drive.
                            </p>
