                                  and lower the base price substantially, the
                                  2024 Lexus RZ becomes more competitive in the
                                  fast-growing small electric crossover segment.
                                  The Lexus RZ is a 5-seater vehicle that comes
                                  in 4 trim levels. The most popular style is
                                  the RZ 300e Premium FWD with 18" wheels, which
                                  starts at $55,150 and comes with an Electric
                                  engine and Front Wheel Drive. This RZ is
