                                          more price competitive, but at the
                                          cost of some of the touches many
                                          luxury buyers seek. But for Lexus
                                          die-hards and buyers who don't need to
                                          drive long distances, the RZ can be a
                                          great choice. Otherwise, we recommend
                                          some comparison shopping.
                                        </p>
