                              well-equipped electric crossover with a very good
                              all-wheel-drive system available. But it is
                              hampered by mediocre driving range and a slow DC
                              fast-charge speed. The Toyota bZ4X is a 5-seater
                              vehicle that comes in 2 trim levels. The most
                              popular style is the XLE AWD, which starts at
                              $46,545 and comes with an Electric engine and All
                              Wheel Drive. This bZ4X is estimated to deliver 114
                              MPGe in the city and 94 MPGe on the highway.
                            </p>
